Tap on other participants avatar in the chat for quick actions. You can now enable or disable call notifications for each conversation. Allow to set user status message. Conversation description is now shown in the lobby. Added an unread mentions indicator to the conversations list. Group mentions are display differently than direct mentions. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Forward chat messages. You can now clear all chat messages in a conversation as a moderator. Added Arabic localization and support for RTL languages. Bug fixes and performance improvements.

Fixed chat notifications delay. Route voice message audio to the correct speaker using proximity sensor. Allow to resend invitations to email participants. Show conversation description. View and edit user profile information. Change profile settings privacy scopes. Allow to change read status privacy setting. Phone number integration is now a per account setting.

Fixed issue which caused missing chat notifications. Incoming calls are now ended if call was picked up in another device or ended by the other peer. Fixed problem sharing files from Nextcloud that were in subfolders. Other bug fixes and performance improvements.
You can now delete chat messages sent by mistake! New call view design. Incoming call notifications now show available audio or video. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Bug fixes and performance improvements.

Dark mode. Added ability to preview edit crop and delete items in share confirmation view. Chat view enhancements and improvements. Fixed display issues and crashes in calling view. Other bug fixes and performance improvements.

Preview shared files in a conversation. Show sent and read status of messages. Added an option to sync your address book contacts with your Nextcloud contacts. Increased the size of only emoji messages. Allow to share up to 5 files using system sharing option. Allow to preview files in file conversations. Fixed missing call icons in chat view on iOS 10 devices. Other bug fixes and performance improvements.
Fixed connection issues in calls using external signaling server. Fixed remaining issue with database migration process in some devices.
Fixed app crash when Theming app is disabled in your Nextcloud server. Fixed issue with database migration process.

The app now adapts its interface to your Nextcloud theming color. Directly reply to chat messages notifications. Added Push to talk feature in calls. Take a picture and share it directly from the app. Added German Italian and Spanish localization more languages will be added soon... Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Fixed image orientation on images picked from in app image picker. Fixed chat position when entering a conversation with unread messages. Other bug fixes and performance improvements.

Talk now has offline support! Read your chats without internet like when you are on a train or a plane! Want to share a link while calling You can now access the chat while in a call! Don t like feedback Participants can now get muted by moderators. Accessibility enhancements and bug fixes as always. Thanks for your issue reports!
